日产聆风提供两个充电装置，一种是北美标准[[SAE_J1772|SAE J1772-2009]]连接器（120/220V交流电）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://green.autoblog.com/2010/04/09/nissan-and-aerovironment-show-off-prototype-leaf-home-charger/ |title=Nissan and AeroVironment show off prototype $2,200 Leaf home charger |author=Eric Loveday |date=2010-04-09 |publisher=Autoblog Green |accessdate=2010-04-13 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126124622/http://green.autoblog.com/2010/04/09/nissan-and-aerovironment-show-off-prototype-leaf-home-charger/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，另一种是由[[东京电力公司|东京电力公司]]为直流快速充电设计的高压直流连接器（500V直流电，125安培）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.greencarcongress.com/2010/01/akerwade-20100115.html |title=Tokyo Electric Power Licenses Aker Wade to Build Level III Fast Chargers |date=2010-01-15 |publisher=Green Car Congress |accessdate=2010-04-13 |archive-date=2010-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100122110020/http://www.greencarcongress.com/2010/01/akerwade-20100115.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，上述充电插座使用[[CHAdeMO|CHAdeMO]]协议<ref name="cars21 akee">{{cite web |url=http://www.cars21.com/content/articles/2010-04-29-exclusive-interview-with-bret-aker--standardisation-is-the-key.php |title=Exclusive interview with the CEO of Aker Wade: "Standardisation is the key" |date=2010-04-29 |publisher=cars21.com |accessdate=2010-05-13 |archive-date=2018-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180712083854/http://www.cars21.com/content/articles/2010-04-29-exclusive-interview-with-bret-aker--standardisation-is-the-key.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

该车有两种充电方法，即普通充电及快速充电<ref name="充电方法">{{cite web|url=http://www.nissan.com.cn/minisite/leaf/Charge.php|title=充电方法 > 充电|publisher=日产中国|accessdate=2015年11月25日|archive-date=2016年5月5日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160505004216/http://www.nissan.com.cn/minisite/leaf/Charge.php|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。普通充电的方法为利用普通的家用插头充电<ref name="充电方法"/>。对于3.6KW的充电器，普通充电时间为8小时<ref>{{cite web|last=Nissan|title=Nissan LEAF Electric Car {{!}} The New Car – Features and Specifications|url=http://www.nissanusa.com/leaf-electric-car/tags/show/range#/leaf-electric-car/specs-features/index|accessdate=2010-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100427004517/http://www.nissanusa.com/leaf-electric-car/tags/show/range#/leaf-electric-car/specs-features/index|archive-date=2010-04-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="nissan-faq-charging">{{cite web |url=http://www.nissanusa.com/leaf-electric-car/faq/list/charging#/leaf-electric-car/faq/list/charging |title=Nissan LEAF Electric Car | Answers | Charging |publisher=Nissan |accessdate=2010-05-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100424143119/http://www.nissanusa.com/leaf-electric-car/faq/list/charging#/leaf-electric-car/faq/list/charging |archivedate=2010年4月24日 |df= }}</ref><ref name=NissanEVplans>{{cite web |first=Christopher |last=Sawyer |url=http://www.autofieldguide.com/articles/020903.html |publisher=Automotive Design and Production |title=Nissan's EV and Battery Plans |date=February 2009 |accessdate=2009-10-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100331131832/http://www.autofieldguide.com/articles/020903.html |archivedate=2010-03-31 }}</ref> ；而对于6.6KW的充电器，普通充电时间为4小时（以上为理论值，实际充电时间因气温与电源状态的不同而有所差异）<ref name="nissan-faq-charging" /><ref name=NissanEVplans/>。快速充电的方法为在外出的时候，使用专门的充电设备进行快速充电<ref name="充电方法"/>，在30分钟内可充满80%的电<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.wired.com/autopia/2009/08/nissan-electric-leaf/ |title=Nissan Turns Over An Electric Leaf |date=2009-09-02 |author=Chuck Squatriglia |work=Wired News |accessdate=2010-05-13 |archive-date=2014-01-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103001930/http://www.wired.com/autopia/2009/08/nissan-electric-leaf/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。日产汽车所研发的专门的充电设备的售价为147万日元，并计划在200家经销商安装专门的充电设备<ref name=QuickCharger>{{cite web |url=http://www.nissan-global.com/EN/NEWS/2010/_STORY/100521-01-e.html |title=Nissan Introduces Quick EV Charger |publisher=Nissan Global Website |date=2010-05-21 |accessdate=2010-05-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100524101734/http://www.nissan-global.com/EN/NEWS/2010/_STORY/100521-01-e.html |archivedate=2010-05-24 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://green.autoblog.com/2010/05/21/nissan-announces-49-kw-quick-charger-for-evs/2#c28103204 |title=Nissan announces 49 kW quick charger for EVs |author=Sam Abuelsamid |date=2010-05-21 |publisher=Autoblog Green |accessdate=2010-05-25 |archive-date=2020-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813003447/http://green.autoblog.com/2010/05/21/nissan-announces-49-kw-quick-charger-for-evs/2#c28103204 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===仪表盘===
日产聆风使用高分辨率彩色液晶屏，采用与[[本田思域|本田思域]]相似的双层式布局，可显示车速、功率、能量回收状态、电池组温度、行驶时间、单次行驶里程、时钟、车外温度等常规信息及估计续航里程，同时可通过导航系统提供临近充电站的位置和距离等信息<ref name="中文名"/>。

===安全性===
根据[[美国国家公路交通安全管理局|美国国家公路交通安全管理局]]的撞击测试报告，2011/12款聆风获得五星安全评价，2013/14款聆风由于正面及侧面碰撞测试得分较低，仅获得四星安全评价<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.safercar.gov/Vehicle+Shoppers/5-Star+Safety+Ratings/2011-Newer+Vehicles/Search-Results?searchtype=model&make=NISSAN&model=LEAF&year=|title=2011 & Newer - Search Results Safercar -- National Highway Traffic Safety Administration (NHTSA)|accessdate=2015年11月28日|archive-date=2016年8月9日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160809045150/http://www.safercar.gov/Vehicle+Shoppers/5-Star+Safety+Ratings/2011-Newer+Vehicles/Search-Results?searchtype=model&make=NISSAN&model=LEAF&year=|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而根据[[欧盟新车安全评鉴协会|欧盟新车安全评鉴协会]]的撞击测试报告，聆风获得五星安全评价<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.euroncap.com/files/432_datasheet.pdf|title=Euro NCAP报告|accessdate=2015年11月28日|archive-date=2012年12月12日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121212111442/http://www.euroncap.com/files/432_datasheet.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[File:Nissan_Leaf_warning_sound_switch_trimmed.jpg|thumb]]
