中国大陆方面，中国政府曾与日产在中国的合资子公司[[东风日产|东风日产]]签订协议生产日产聆风，计划年生产10,000辆，预计到2015年將年生产50,000辆<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-03-14/nissan-may-build-leaf-cars-in-china-government-site-says.html|title=Nissan May Build Leaf Cars in China, Government Site Says|author=Bloomberg News|work=[[Bloomberg_L.P.|Bloomberg]]|date=2013-03-15|accessdate=2013-03-19|archive-date=2014-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222154416/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-03-14/nissan-may-build-leaf-cars-in-china-government-site-says.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但实际上[[东风日产|东风日产]]并没有生产聆风，而是生产与聆风同平台研发的[[启辰|启辰]]晨风（e30，详见“启辰晨风（e30）”一节）。

==销售==
2010年12月3日，日产汽车在[[横滨市|横滨市]]总部宣布，聆风于当日起在日本开始销售<ref name=LaunchJap>{{cite web|last=Kageyama|first=Yuri|title=Nissan rolls out Leaf electric car in Japan|date=2010-12-03|url=http://www.physorg.com/news/2010-12-nissan-leaf-electric-car-japan.html|publisher=Associated Press|accessdate=2011-05-31}}</ref>。12月11日，美国[[北加州|北加州]]消费者成為全球第一台日产聆风的車主<ref name=LaunchUS>{{cite news|url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/nissan-makes-history-with-delivery-of-worlds-first-100-electric-nissan-leaf-to-california-consumer-111725479.html?utm_source=twitterfeed&utm_medium=twitter|title=Nissan Makes History With Delivery of World's First 100% Electric Nissan LEAF to California Consumer|agency=PR Newswire|author=[[Nissan|Nissan]]|date=2010-12-11|accessdate=2010-12-11|archive-date=2012-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120713200712/http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/nissan-makes-history-with-delivery-of-worlds-first-100-electric-nissan-leaf-to-california-consumer-111725479.html?utm_source=twitterfeed&utm_medium=twitter|dead-url=no}}</ref>；12月22日，[[神奈川縣|神奈川縣]]的消费者成为日本首位聆风车主<ref name=JapanDeliver1>{{cite news|url=http://www.thegreencarwebsite.co.uk/blog/index.php/2010/12/22/nissan-delivers-first-leaf-in-japan/|title=Nissan delivers first Leaf in Japan|publisher=The Green Car Website|date=2010-12-22|accessdate=2010-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101226174736/http://www.thegreencarwebsite.co.uk/blog/index.php/2010/12/22/nissan-delivers-first-leaf-in-japan|archive-date=2010-12-26|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。在2010年－2012年间，日产聆风先后被爱尔兰、英国、法国、葡萄牙、荷兰、加拿大、西班牙、挪威、瑞士和德国消费者交付<ref name=NFrance>{{cite web|url=http://green.autoblog.com/2011/08/08/nissan-celebrates-first-leaf-delivery-in-france/|title=Nissan celebrates first Leaf delivery in France|author=Nissan Press Release|publisher=AutoblogGreen|date=2011-08-08|accessdate=2011-08-08|archive-date=2020-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809114149/http://green.autoblog.com/2011/08/08/nissan-celebrates-first-leaf-delivery-in-france/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=IREfirst>{{cite web|url=http://www.nissan.ie/NissanLeaf/NissanLeafScience/news_details.aspx?id=1203|title=Nissan to Make History with Delivery of Europe's First 100% Electric Nissan Leaf to Kerry Customer|publisher=Nissan Ireland|date=2011-02-28|accessdate=2011-03-21|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110914130150/http://www.nissan.ie/NissanLeaf/NissanLeafScience/news_details.aspx?id=1203|archivedate=2011-09-14}}</ref><ref name=UKfirst>{{cite web|url=http://www.whatcar.com/car-news/nissan-leaf-deliveries-start-in-uk/256080|title=Nissan Leaf deliveries start in UK|publisher=What a Car?|date=2011-03-21|accessdate=2011-03-21|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110324125352/http://www.whatcar.com/car-news/nissan-leaf-deliveries-start-in-uk/256080|archivedate=2011-03-24}}</ref><ref name=PORfirst>{{cite web|url=http://www.thegreencarwebsite.co.uk/blog/index.php/2010/12/23/electric-leaf-makes-european-debut-in-portugal/|title=Electric Leaf makes European debut in Portugal|publisher=The Green Car Website|date=2010-12-23|accessdate=2010-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101226174741/http://www.thegreencarwebsite.co.uk/blog/index.php/2010/12/23/electric-leaf-makes-european-debut-in-portugal|archive-date=2010-12-26|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name=NEDdel>{{cite web|url=http://www.nissaninthenews.com/nissan-leaf-hits-the-road-in-the-netherlands/|title=Nissan Leaf Hits The Road In The Netherlands|work=Nissan in the News|publisher=Nissan|date=2011-03-25|accessdate=2011-05-19|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110505035016/http://www.nissaninthenews.com/nissan-leaf-hits-the-road-in-the-netherlands/|archivedate=2011-05-05}}</ref><ref name=CANissan>{{cite web|url=http://www.nissaninthenews.com/first-nissan-leaf-ev-arrives-in-canada/ |title=First Nissan Leaf EV Arrives In Canada |publisher=Nissan in the News |date=2011-07-29 |accessdate=2011-07-31 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120324062801/http://www.nissaninthenews.com/first-nissan-leaf-ev-arrives-in-canada/ |archivedate=2012-03-24 }}</ref>。

[[中国大陆|中国大陆]]方面，2011年9月，日产称将于2011年10月起开始在中国大陆市场销售日产聆风，售价拟定为人民币20万元<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/09/13/us-nissan-idUSTRE78C0UW20110913|title=Nissan gets OK to sell electric car Leaf in China|author=Mayumi Negishi|work=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|date=2011-09-13|accessdate=2011-09-15|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924155202/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/09/13/us-nissan-idUSTRE78C0UW20110913|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name=NChina>{{cite web|url=http://green.autoblog.com/2011/09/15/nissan-sell-leaf-china/|title=Nissan now approved to sell Leaf in China|author=Eric Loveday|publisher=AutoblogGreen|date=2011-09-15|accessdate=2011-09-15|archive-date=2020-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812235924/http://green.autoblog.com/2011/09/15/nissan-sell-leaf-china/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.chinacartimes.com/2011/09/13/nissans-leaf-to-be-imported-into-china-after-oct-1st-holiday/|title=Nissan's Leaf to be imported into China after October 1st Holiday|work=China Car Times|date=2011-09-13|accessdate=2011-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120728002353/http://www.chinacartimes.com/2011/09/13/nissans-leaf-to-be-imported-into-china-after-oct-1st-holiday/|archive-date=2012-07-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。起初，日产聆风仅面向政府客户销售，且数量有限<ref>{{cite news|url=http://in.reuters.com/article/businessNews/idINIndia-47546620100408?pageNumber=1&virtualBrandChannel=0|title=Nissan to sell Leaf in China in 2011|publisher=Reuters|date=2010-04-08|accessdate=2010-04-24}}</ref>。在2011年11月，日产向[[武汉市|武汉市]][[武汉市人民政府|人民政府]]交付了首批15辆日产聆风，第二批的10辆于2012年交付使用<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.greencarcongress.com/2011/11/wuhan-20111119.html|title=Nissan and Wuhan Municipal Government moving forward on electromobility pilot program|publisher=Green Car Congress|date=2011-11-19|accessdate=2011-11-30|archive-date=2020-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200918213318/https://www.greencarcongress.com/2011/11/wuhan-20111119.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nissan.com.cn/minisite/leaf/inchina_cont.php?year=0&area=0&id=56|title=日产汽车向武汉市政府交付首批纯电动汽车日产聆风 进一步推动电动汽车示范项目发展|publisher=日产中国|accessdate=2015年11月27日|archive-date=2016年5月16日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160516072221/http://www.nissan.com.cn/minisite/leaf/inchina_cont.php?year=0&area=0&id=56|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。同年12月8日，日产向[[广州市|广州市]][[广州市人民政府|人民政府]]赠送了15辆日产聆风、2台快速充电器，另外广州市政府已经以市区为中心设置了15台普通充电器<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nissan.com.cn/minisite/leaf/inchina_cont.php?year=0&area=0&id=60|title=日产汽车与东风汽车有限向广州市政府赠送纯电动汽车“日产聆风”|publisher=日产中国|accessdate=2015年11月27日|archive-date=2016年5月7日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507182815/http://www.nissan.com.cn/minisite/leaf/inchina_cont.php?year=0&area=0&id=60|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。目前，日产聆风出租车在广州市[[花都区|花都区]]行政范围内运营，车身为黄、红两色<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ycwb.com/epaper/ycwb/html/2012-09/12/content_1488398.htm|title=广州首批电动出租车现花都|publisher=羊城晚报|date=2012年9月12日|accessdate=2015年11月28日|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120913042053/http://www.ycwb.com/ePaper/ycwb/html/2012-09/12/content_1488398.htm|archivedate=2012年9月13日}}</ref>。香港方面，日产在2011年3月引进聆风，计划向政府、电力公司和其他私人公司出售200辆<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nissan.com.hk/en/web/news/LEAF_GRAND_LAUNCH.htm|title=Hong Kong Government Begins EV Pilot Program with Nissan LEAF|date=2010-03-24|publisher=Nissan Hong Kong|accessdate=2011-03-25|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111006142953/http://www.nissan.com.hk/en/web/news/LEAF_GRAND_LAUNCH.htm|archivedate=2011-10-06}}</ref>，2012年已出售89辆<ref>{{cite web|url=http://bestsellingcarsblog.com/2013/01/20/hong-kong-china-full-year-2012-mercedes-e-class-most-popular-bmw-5-series-on-podium/|title=Hong Kong (China) Full Year 2012: Mercedes E-Class most popular,BMW 5 Series on podium|author=Mat Gasnier|publisher=Best Selling Car Blog|date=2013-01-20|accessdate=2013-01-22|archive-date=2013-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130123222536/http://bestsellingcarsblog.com/2013/01/20/hong-kong-china-full-year-2012-mercedes-e-class-most-popular-bmw-5-series-on-podium/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在[[台灣|台灣]]，日產Leaf第一代被一些政府機關少量採購作為公務用車，例如[[台中市政府|台中市政府]]<ref name=carstuff-20190803>{{cite news |url=https://www.carstuff.com.tw/car-news/item/29541-nissan-leaf.html |title=世界最暢銷電動車到底有何魅力？第二代 Nissan Leaf 展示間搶先預賞！ |publisher=CarStuff |date=2019-08-03 |accessdate=2019-11-18 |archive-date=2019-08-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190805052004/https://www.carstuff.com.tw/car-news/item/29541-nissan-leaf.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2019年，[[裕隆日產汽車|裕隆日產汽車]]正式引進第二代銷售給一般消費者，建議售價新台幣149萬元<ref name=carstuff-20190803 />。

