日产聆风曾参加2011年的[[派克峰国际爬山赛|派克峰国际爬山赛]]（电动车组）<ref>{{cite web|title=Nissan at Pikes Peak|url=http://www.motorweek.org/auto_news/motor_news/nissan_at_pikes_peak|publisher=Motor Week|accessdate=2012-11-21|archive-date=2020-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200708214347/https://www.motorweek.org/auto_news/motor_news/nissan_at_pikes_peak|dead-url=no}}</ref>。最终，日产聆风以14分33秒的成绩夺冠，总赛程为{{convert|12.42|mi|km|abbr=in|disp=flip}}<ref name="CNET Pikes Peak">{{cite web|last=Cunningham|first=Wayne|title=Nissan Leaf wins its division in Pike's Peak race|url=http://reviews.cnet.com/8301-13746_7-20074880-48/nissan-leaf-wins-its-division-in-pikes-peak-race/|publisher=[[CNET|CNET]]|accessdate=2012-11-21|archive-date=2014-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222052405/http://reviews.cnet.com/8301-13746_7-20074880-48/nissan-leaf-wins-its-division-in-pikes-peak-race/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。为了更好的发挥，车内所有的内饰全部被卸下，并更换为专用赛车座椅、安全带和防滚架<ref>{{cite web|last=Sanchez|first=Karla|title=They Won’t Hear This Coming: Nissan Leaf Will Race Pikes Peak|url=http://wot.motortrend.com/wont-hear-coming-nissan-leaf-will-race-pikes-peak-83025.html#axzz2CpJmbzqC|publisher=Motor Trend|accessdate=2012-11-21|archive-date=2015-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150610130908/http://wot.motortrend.com/wont-hear-coming-nissan-leaf-will-race-pikes-peak-83025.html#axzz2CpJmbzqC|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==评价==
日产聆风一直受到消费者的追捧和热爱，深受好评。该车发布后，在美国有2万辆预购订单<ref>{{cite web|last=Loveday|first=Eric|title=Nissan reaches 20,000 Leaf pre-orders; will stop taking reservations|url=http://green.autoblog.com/2010/09/23/report-nissan-reaches-20-000-leaf-pre-orders-will-stop-taking/|publisher=AutoBlogGreen|accessdate=2011-02-27|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126124621/http://green.autoblog.com/2010/09/23/report-nissan-reaches-20-000-leaf-pre-orders-will-stop-taking/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

聆风曾先后获得多个机构主办的奖项。在2010年[[华盛顿车展|华盛顿车展]]上，日产聆风获得了{{link-en|绿色汽车远见奖|Green Car Vision Award}}（Green Car Vision Award）<ref name=GreenAward>{{cite web|url=http://www.greencar.com/articles/nissan-leaf-electric-car-wins-2010-green-car-vision-award.php|publisher=Green Car Journal|title=Nissan Leaf Electric Car Wins 2010 Green Car Vision Award|author=Green Car Journal Editors|date=2010-01-26|accessdate=2010-01-27|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100504162701/http://www.greencar.com/articles/nissan-leaf-electric-car-wins-2010-green-car-vision-award.php|archivedate=2010-05-04}}</ref>；在此之后，该车又先后获得了2011年[[欧洲年度风云车|欧洲年度风云车]]大奖<ref name=ECOTY>{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/motoring/news/8167962/Nissan-Leaf-wins-Car-of-the-Year.html|title=Nissan Leaf wins Car of the Year|accessdate=2010-11-29|work=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]]|location=London|first=Andrew|last=English|date=2010-11-29|archive-date=2018-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180713082936/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/motoring/news/8167962/Nissan-Leaf-wins-Car-of-the-Year.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>、2011年年度电动汽车大奖<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ev.com/knowledge-center/ev-coms-2011-ev-of-the-year.html|title=EV.com’s 2011 EV of the Year|publisher=EV.com|date=2010-12-26|accessdate=2011-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110704083136/http://www.ev.com/knowledge-center/ev-coms-2011-ev-of-the-year.html|archive-date=2011-07-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>、2011年年度生态友好车大奖<ref>{{cite web|url=http://green.autoblog.com/2011/10/25/nissan-leaf-wins-2011-greenfleet-electric-vehicle-of-the-year/|title=Nissan Leaf wins 2011 GreenFleet "Electric Vehicle of the Year" award|author=Eric Loveday|publisher=AutoblogGreen|date=2011-10-25|accessdate=2011-10-26|archive-date=2020-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126132111/http://green.autoblog.com/2011/10/25/nissan-leaf-wins-2011-greenfleet-electric-vehicle-of-the-year/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、2011年[[世界年度风云车|世界年度风云车]]大奖<ref name=WCOTY>{{cite web|url=http://www.wcoty.com/web/media_release.asp?release=69&year=2011|title=Nissan Leaf Declared 2011 World Car Of The Year|publisher=World Car of the Year|date=2011-04-24|accessdate=2011-04-24|archive-date=2018-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180712053050/http://www.wcoty.com/web/media_release.asp?release=69&year=2011|dead-url=no}}</ref>以及2011-2012年度[[日本年度风云车|日本年度风云车]]大奖等<ref name=JapAward>{{cite news|url=http://www.france24.com/en/20111203-nissan-leaf-electric-wins-japan-car-year|title=Nissan Leaf electric wins Japan car of the year|author=AFP|publisher=France 24|date=2011-12-03|accessdate=2011-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111215015323/http://www.france24.com/en/20111203-nissan-leaf-electric-wins-japan-car-year|archive-date=2011-12-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。该车亦被《[[时代周刊|时代周刊]]》列入“2009年五十大最佳发明”之一<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,1934027_1934003_1933970,00.html|title=The 50 Best Inventions of 2009|work=[[Time_(magazine)|Time Magazine]]|accessdate=2009-11-13|date=2009-11-12|archive-date=2013-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130826211005/http://www.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,1934027_1934003_1933970,00.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

另外，日产聆风的EM61型[[永磁同步马达|永磁同步马达]]亦获得了由美国《华德汽车世界》主办的2011年的[[华德十大最佳汽车引擎|华德十大最佳汽车引擎]]奖<ref>{{cite web|url=http://wardsauto.com/ar/names_best_engines_101207/|title=Ward’s Names 10 Best Engines Winners|author=Tom Murphy|accessdate=2015年11月28日|archive-date=2015年10月12日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151012124957/http://wardsauto.com/ar/names_best_engines_101207|dead-url=no}}</ref>（日产此前在1995年-2008年（连续14年，VQ系列发动机）及2009年（VR DOHC双涡轮增压发动机）获得该奖项）。

